Company Overview of Anadarko Marcellus Midstream, L.L.C.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Anadarko Marcellus Midstream, L.L.C. constructs and operates midstream infrastructure such as pad facilities and flow lines, large diameter pipelines, compression facilities and downstream interconnects. The company was incorporated in 2008 is based in The Woodlands, Texas. Anadarko Marcellus Midstream, L.L.C. operates as a subsidiary of Anadarko Petroleum Corporation.


